bnf_parser

Class Rule.CallableContainer

  • java.lang.Object
    • bnf_parser.Rule.CallableContainer
  • Enclosing class:
    Rule

    protected class Rule.CallableContainer
extends java.lang.Object
    Inner class which acts as a container for every Callable. It allows to specify a custom index for a specific Callable which will be used by a Collector to distinguish different Collector's.
    Author:
    Hubert Lemelin
